      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、愛ちゃん～\n朝から筋トレなんて偉いなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Ai-chan~\nIt's great to do strength training in the morning",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、筋トレは趣味なんです！\n良かったら優ちゃんも一緒にやりませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ strength training is my hobby!\nIf you'd like‚ would you like to join me‚ Yu-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9833.333333300001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあご一緒させてもらおうかな～\nよいしょっと……隣、失礼するな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ let's do it together~\nHeave-ho… excuse me‚ sitting next to you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "（優ちゃんが寝転んだ瞬間、なんかふわぁって）\n（いい香りしたんだけど。ふわぁってこれ何！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The moment Yu-chan lay down‚ I smelled）\n（something really good. What's this!?）",
        "id": ""
