      "startTime": 32.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "（素敵だな～。シャンプーかな？　私もこんな風に）\n（お嬢様みたいな香りを纏ってみたい……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That's lovely~. Is it shampoo? I also want to）\n（give off a girly scent like this…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "（……あれ？　優ちゃんさっきから私のことを）\n（じっと見てる……何か言いたそうだけど……はっ！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Huh? Yu-chan has been looking at me）\n（for a while now… she seems to have something to say… oh!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "も、もしかして、私汗くさいですか！？\nごめんなさい、ごめんなさいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-Does my sweat smell‚ bad?\nI'm sorry‚ I'm sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
