      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "（そういえば、海の日の水着撮影の時の）\n（優ちゃんの身体……凄く綺麗で……胸も……）",
